{
  "info": {
    "name": "POS Hono API",
    "_postman_id": "pos-hono-collection",
    "description": "Koleksi Postman buat POS Hono API (Bun + Hono + PostgreSQL). Login pakai JWT access token + refresh token (cookie httpOnly). Habis Login/Register/Refresh, accessToken-nya otomatis kesimpen ke variable koleksi, jadi request lain tinggal pakai {{accessToken}} — nggak usah copy-paste manual.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "midtransServerKey",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Isi sama MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY yang dipakai server — dipakai buat ngitung signature webhook simulasi."
    },
    {
      "key": "xenditCallbackToken",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Isi sama XENDIT_CALLBACK_TOKEN yang dipakai server — dipakai di header webhook simulasi."
    },
    {
      "key": "paymentId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "paymentExternalRef",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "paymentAmount",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Keisi otomatis pas Login (cashier) — target buat Set PIN."
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (cashier)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', json.data.user.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/register",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "register"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"kasir.baru@pos.test\",\n  \"password\": \"Rahasia123!\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Kasir Baru\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Daftar user baru. Otomatis jadi role `cashier`. Balikannya accessToken + cookie refresh token (httpOnly) langsung kepasang. Id user barunya kesimpen ke {{userId}} — jadi habis ini bisa langsung Login (admin) → Users/Set PIN tanpa copy-paste. Email harus unik (409 kalau dobel)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@pos.test\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123!\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Login. Akun buat nyoba: admin@pos.test / Admin123! (admin) atau kasir@pos.test / Kasir123! (kasir). accessToken-nya otomatis kesimpen ke variable koleksi."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (cashier)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', json.data.user.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"kasir@pos.test\",\n  \"password\": \"Kasir123!\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai kasir buat ngetes RBAC — coba bikin produk nanti pasti kena 403, soalnya kasir nggak punya izinnya. Id user-nya kesimpen ke variable {{userId}} (dipakai request Set PIN)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PIN login (cashier switch)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/pin-login",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "pin-login"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{userId}}\",\n  \"pin\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Login cepat pakai PIN (layar ganti kasir). Urutan nyobanya: Login (cashier) buat ngisi {{userId}} → Login (admin) → Users/Set PIN → request ini. Balikannya sama kayak login biasa; accessToken otomatis kesimpen. Salah PIN / user tanpa PIN = 401. Kena rate limit 5 req/menit."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/refresh",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "refresh"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Tuker refresh token (dari cookie httpOnly yang diurus Postman otomatis) jadi accessToken baru. Refresh token yang lama langsung dimatiin (rotation)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/me",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "me"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Ngambil data user dari access token yang lagi aktif."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/logout",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "auth",
                "logout"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Matiin refresh token sama hapus cookie-nya. Balikannya 204 (kosong)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Products",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List products",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products?limit=100&offset=0",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "products"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "100"
                },
                {
                  "key": "offset",
                  "value": "0"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Liat daftar produk (paginasi offset). Butuh izin products:read (admin sama kasir dua-duanya punya). limit default 100 maks 100, offset default 0. meta ngasih total + hasMore — lanjut halaman berikutnya dengan offset += limit."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get product by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products/p_kopi",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "products",
                "p_kopi"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Ngambil satu produk. Kalau nggak ada, kena 404."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create product (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "products"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"p_donat\",\n  \"sku\": \"FD-003\",\n  \"name\": \"Donat Gula\",\n  \"price\": 7000,\n  \"stock\": 40\n}"
            },
            "description": "Bikin produk baru. Butuh izin products:write (cuma admin). Kalau login-nya kasir, bakal kena 403. Harga ditulis dalam rupiah bulat (integer)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update product (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products/p_donat",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "products",
                "p_donat"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"price\": 8000,\n  \"stock\": 60\n}"
            },
            "description": "Update sebagian field produk aja. Butuh products:write. Minimal isi satu field."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Checkout",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create checkout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "{{$guid}}",
                "description": "Wajib diisi. Kalau mau retry, pakai nilai yang sama biar nggak kena charge dobel."
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/checkout",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "checkout"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productId\": \"p_kopi\", \"quantity\": 2 },\n    { \"productId\": \"p_nasi\", \"quantity\": 1 }\n  ],\n  \"discount\": { \"type\": \"percentage\", \"value\": 10 },\n  \"payments\": [\n    { \"method\": \"cash\", \"amount\": 100000 }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "description": "Proses transaksi jualan. Butuh izin checkout:create. Header Idempotency-Key WAJIB; kalau dikirim ulang pakai key yang sama, dia balikin struk yang sama persis (200, header Idempotent-Replay: true) tanpa bikin transaksi baru. Stok dikurangin secara atomik pakai row lock biar nggak oversell. Diskon opsional (percentage 0-100 atau fixed). PPN 11% dihitung setelah diskon. Total dibulatin ke Rp 100 terdekat. payments boleh lebih dari satu (bayar campur)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List users (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/users?limit=20&offset=0",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "users"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                },
                {
                  "key": "offset",
                  "value": "0"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Semua akun buat layar manajemen staf (paginasi offset, limit default 20 maks 100). Butuh users:manage (cuma admin). meta: total/limit/offset/hasMore."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Set PIN (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/users/{{userId}}/pin",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "users",
                "{{userId}}",
                "pin"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"pin\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Set/ganti PIN user (4-6 digit). Butuh users:manage (cuma admin) — kalau kena 403 padahal login admin, login ulang dulu biar permission barunya masuk ke token. {{userId}} keisi otomatis pas Login (cashier), atau isi manual. Balikannya 204."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List users with PIN",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/users/with-pin",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "users",
                "with-pin"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Semua user yang udah punya PIN — buat layar pemilihan kasir. Cukup login (role apa aja). PIN-nya sendiri nggak pernah dibalikin (di-hash bcrypt)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Payments (Midtrans / Xendit)",
      "description": "Bayar online lewat gateway. Alurnya: Create payment → customer bayar di paymentUrl → gateway manggil webhook → status jadi paid. Buat ngetes lokal (gateway nggak bisa nembak localhost), pakai request 'Simulate webhook' — signature/token-nya dihitung otomatis. Syarat: server jalan dengan MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY / XENDIT_SECRET_KEY + XENDIT_CALLBACK_TOKEN keisi, dan variable koleksi midtransServerKey / xenditCallbackToken diisi nilai yang sama.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create payment (Midtrans)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('paymentId', json.data.id);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('paymentExternalRef', json.data.externalRef);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('paymentAmount', String(json.data.amount));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "{{$guid}}",
                "description": "Wajib. Kirim ulang pakai nilai sama = replay payment yang sama (nggak bikin tagihan baru)."
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "payments"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"provider\": \"midtrans\",\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productId\": \"p_kopi\", \"quantity\": 2 }\n  ],\n  \"discount\": { \"type\": \"percentage\", \"value\": 10 }\n}"
            },
            "description": "Bikin tagihan Midtrans Snap. Nggak ada field amount — server yang ngitung total (aturan sama kayak checkout). Balikannya paymentUrl (halaman Snap) buat customer. id, externalRef, dan amount otomatis kesimpen ke variable koleksi buat request berikutnya. Butuh MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY keisi di server; kalau belum, kena 503."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create payment (Xendit)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('paymentId', json.data.id);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('paymentExternalRef', json.data.externalRef);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('paymentAmount', String(json.data.amount));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "{{$guid}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "payments"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"provider\": \"xendit\",\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productId\": \"p_teh\", \"quantity\": 3 }\n  ],\n  \"customerEmail\": \"budi@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Bikin invoice Xendit. Balikannya paymentUrl (halaman invoice) buat customer. Butuh XENDIT_SECRET_KEY + XENDIT_CALLBACK_TOKEN keisi di server; kalau belum, kena 503."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get payment status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/{{paymentId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "payments",
                "{{paymentId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Polling status dari layar kasir. pending → paid begitu webhook masuk; transactionId keisi id transaksi (struk) yang dibikin mesin checkout."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Simulate webhook — Midtrans settlement",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const CryptoJS = require('crypto-js');",
                  "const orderId = pm.collectionVariables.get('paymentExternalRef');",
                  "const amount = pm.collectionVariables.get('paymentAmount');",
                  "const serverKey = pm.collectionVariables.get('midtransServerKey');",
                  "if (!orderId || !amount) throw new Error('Jalanin \"Create payment (Midtrans)\" dulu.');",
                  "if (!serverKey) throw new Error('Isi variable koleksi midtransServerKey dulu (samain dengan MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY server).');",
                  "const gross = amount + '.00';",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('midtransGrossAmount', gross);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('midtransSignature', CryptoJS.SHA512(orderId + '200' + gross + serverKey).toString());"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/webhooks/midtrans",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "payments",
                "webhooks",
                "midtrans"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"order_id\": \"{{paymentExternalRef}}\",\n  \"status_code\": \"200\",\n  \"gross_amount\": \"{{midtransGrossAmount}}\",\n  \"signature_key\": \"{{midtransSignature}}\",\n  \"transaction_status\": \"settlement\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Pura-pura jadi Midtrans yang ngabarin pembayaran sukses (settlement). Signature SHA-512 dihitung otomatis di pre-request script dari variable midtransServerKey. Habis ini cek 'Get payment status' — harusnya paid + transactionId keisi, dan stok kepotong. Kirim dua kali? Aman, nggak bikin transaksi dobel."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Simulate webhook — Xendit PAID",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('paymentExternalRef')) throw new Error('Jalanin \"Create payment (Xendit)\" dulu.');",
                  "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('xenditCallbackToken')) throw new Error('Isi variable koleksi xenditCallbackToken dulu (samain dengan XENDIT_CALLBACK_TOKEN server).');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-callback-token",
                "value": "{{xenditCallbackToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/webhooks/xendit",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "payments",
                "webhooks",
                "xendit"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"external_id\": \"{{paymentExternalRef}}\",\n  \"status\": \"PAID\",\n  \"paid_amount\": {{paymentAmount}}\n}"
            },
            "description": "Pura-pura jadi Xendit yang ngabarin invoice kebayar. Cuma butuh header x-callback-token yang cocok. Habis ini cek 'Get payment status' — harusnya paid + transactionId keisi."
          }
        }
